Someone here has to work.

21:06.766 --> 21:08.976
I mean, the two of you

21:06.766 --> 21:08.976
just run off

21:09.018 --> 21:11.104
to do your little

21:09.018 --> 21:11.104
decorating project

21:11.145 --> 21:12.646
