21:11.145 --> 21:12.646
here alone.

21:12.688 --> 21:14.732
Michel, did you actually

21:12.688 --> 21:14.732
hear a noise?

21:14.774 --> 21:16.234
Of course I heard a noise.

21:16.275 --> 21:18.694
It was a thwap or a boom.

21:18.736 --> 21:20.154
Gotta go, Michel.

21:20.196 --> 21:21.948
What's the matter?

21:21.989 --> 21:24.408
Apparently, Batman's

21:21.989 --> 21:24.408
